            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Runic 2.2.5</h2>
<ul>
<li>Usage: stop hiding high-usage days — days with very large token totals (cache reads can run to hundreds of millions per day) were wrongly quarantined and shown as zero in usage, cost, and timeline panels; real history now renders in full.</li>
</ul>
